[!note] If both included and excluded branches are used, an entry must satisfy the conditions defined in both settings to be included in the message. The included branches condition(s) is checked first. If you set this value using the vdsconfig command line utility on Windows, separate the branches with a comma. E.g. vdsconfig.bat set-connector-property -connectorname o_sead_pcache_proxy\_\_dc_seradiant_dc_dom\_\_seradiantad -propertyid excludedBranches -propertyvalue "\[\\"cn=users,dc=seradiant,dc=dom\\",\\"cn=domain groups,dc=seradiant,dc=dom\\"\]".
